{
  "stem": "3848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It took three days for me to come to the city of Zdolbuniv.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's 12 kilometers from Rowne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because while we were traveling, the German planes used to come and bombard our transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But before when we heard the planes running, we used to stop and disperse until the planes went away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Traveling by train to come to Zdolbuniv to run away from the area of the-- of the invasion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] When I came back to Zdolbuniv, which was only 12 kilometers from the city of Rowne, I decided to go and visit my family.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I walked the 12 kilometers to Rowne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I met my family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was already, I think, June the 25th, 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I saw the whole family, but in the meantime, the city was being bombarded constantly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I asked them to move from one part of the city to another part of the city, the other end, to hide.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe it's more safer over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I took them over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I had to go back to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was assigned a job for 10 o'clock at night to work on the station of Zdolbuniv.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I had to appear for that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "About 8 o'clock in the evening, I said to my mother that I have to leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'll see you back tomorrow, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] because I have to be on the job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If I won't show up and something happens in Russia, they could send you away to Siberia for that or other things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I said to my mother, I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'll see you tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She says, don't go, my son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Stay with us.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
